  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      several studies have investigated healing effect of phenytoin.In this study we investigate
      healing effect of phenytoin mucoadhesive paste comparing to the usual mucoadhesive paste
      after oral biopsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
